  <title>Introduction</title>

  <p><app>Web</app> offers a simple, clean, beautiful view of the
  Web. Powered by WebKit, it displays pages with the same same
  speed and accuracy as other popular browsers.</p>

  <p><app>Web</app> is the application formerly known as
  <app>Epiphany</app>.</p>

